{"id":"40eff6a4-c1d2-41f4-99a8-b197b522353c","title":"1544/12/06: To Giovan Simone and Gismondo","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"d3a45e41-1b8d-41f0-9d0b-cb197cc98cc7","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, December\u00A06th, 1544.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"e428d08e-46b5-43f3-849e-dacec519ce94","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f15a2a8e-c87c-43d8-831e-164ac100afd0","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ebe385a5-cf3c-48ac-a9b9-d170981a536b","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":28,"value":"74bb79fc-1bd2-4eae-9517-317071579b8c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"831cf9c4-b34a-4c99-ab14-5b2dae2393f8","type":"style/superscript","start":21,"end":22,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"cf8a6f76-90d3-4536-aeee-f1172445e8e2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Giovan Simone and Gismondo.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"2d015d17-261f-4004-86d8-e86eb3a7d786","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":28,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"726b44f8-cd29-4de7-b504-8383466d310e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":15,"value":"d8b71a68-0171-4aa5-a446-69fbdbd88655","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1743e83b-c143-4e84-a42c-26ce8490d959","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":28,"value":"5595abc1-b8bc-419c-ab26-b372b1c2093c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bff018ad-fdb7-4cad-bc7a-0ba24ac6c255","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":21,"end":28,"value":"15145605-1781-4161-8087-98058f415f46","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"806cfbb6-7da9-4e8c-9a54-33ed5a6df7f6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"a4fdb222-c6c2-4879-a256-be80ae82fbf9","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"I have been thinking of late that I would invest sums of money from time to time, amounting in all to a thousand crowns, in a wool merchant\u0027s business\u00A0for Lionardo\u0027s benefit, if he behaves himself properly,\u00A0with the understanding that he will not be free to withdraw the money or to convert it to any other\u00A0use without your permission. I have arranged to begin with a sum of 200 crowns, which I will have paid to you in Florence, if ye agree with my suggestion. If ye do so agree, see to it that the money is\u00A0not invested in a precarious concern, for I did not pick the money up in the street. Let me hear what\u00A0ye think of the proposition: ye are in a position to\u00A0judge of Lionardo\u0027s character better than I, and ye can tell me if it would be wise to do as I propose.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"154dc0ac-4173-4d27-9c6e-5c54e2ae0441","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":0,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"eb48cac9-c66c-460f-89f7-5c16232a7503","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":34,"end":34,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f95839f5-022d-45f1-9174-5c535c3e3784","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":104,"end":118,"value":"fc63f148-eb11-413c-a8cc-d1bda4035bc2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d9b561ed-1e8a-41b3-a8b2-f2f92ff1bd02","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":155,"end":162,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0fd435bc-47cc-4d3e-aa96-a14d4feaff4a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":178,"end":179,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"03cf510d-739c-4741-978b-631a54a0770c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":189,"end":195,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"665fdaa8-f2d1-4ce5-ae71-f883633f6d47","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":235,"end"